  <entry>
    <title></title>
    <link href="https://leolichenxi.github.io/2021/06/11/UE4/2.UE4-%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>https://leolichenxi.github.io/2021/06/11/UE4/2.UE4-%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2021-06-11T06:37:09.413Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-20T06:49:16.571Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="新建工程"><a href="#新建工程" class="headerlink" title="新建工程"></a>新建工程</h3><h4 id="NOTE-PROJECT"><a href="#NOTE-PROJECT" class="headerlink" title="NOTE_PROJECT"></a>NOTE_PROJECT</h4><p><a href="https://ue4community.wiki/logging-lgpidy6i">https://ue4community.wiki/logging-lgpidy6i</a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   UE_LOG(LogTemp,Log,TEXT(&quot;1111111111Warning&quot;))</span><br><span class="line">UE_LOG(LogTemp,Warning,TEXT(&quot;1111111111Warning&quot;))</span><br><span class="line">UE_LOG(LogTemp,Error,TEXT(&quot;1111111111Warning&quot;))</span><br><span class="line">UE_LOG(CustomLog,Error,TEXT(&quot;1111111111Warning&quot;))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">GEngine-&gt; AddOnScreenDebugMessage(-1,1,FColor::Red,&quot;AddOnScreenDebugMessage&quot;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">LOG_SCREEN(&quot;LOG_SCREEN&quot;) </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="自定义："><a href="#自定义：" class="headerlink" title="自定义："></a>自定义：</h3><ol><li><p>在.h文件中<br>DECLARE_LOG_CATEGORY_EXTERN(CustomLog, Log, All);<br>在.cpp文件中<br>DEFINE_LOG_CATEGORY(CustomLog);</p></li><li><p>定义#define LOG_SCREEN(text) if(GEngine) GEngine-&gt; AddOnScreenDebugMessage(-1,1,FColor::Red,text);</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
